title: Other plugins by Flibbles

!! ''[[Relink|https://flibbles.github.io/tw5-relink/]]''

Updates all references to your tiddlers when you rename them. //All// references:

* tiddler fields
* widget attributes
* filter operands
* macro parameters
* links and all other wikitext

Highly customizable, but also works as-is from the moment you install it.
